com.github.wuic.servlet

Enum HttpRequestThreadLocal

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<HttpRequestThreadLocal>
      • com.github.wuic.servlet.HttpRequestThreadLocal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<HttpRequestThreadLocal>, Runnable

    public enum HttpRequestThreadLocal
extends Enum<HttpRequestThreadLocal>
implements Runnable

    Tool that can be used to bind to a ThreadLocal an HTTP request state to know if GZIP is supported and then write according to this information a ConvertibleNut to the HTTP response.

    Since:
    0.5.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Guillaume DROUET
